  "title": "Audit Manager #75376",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Audit Firm/CPA Firm</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Audit Manager</strong></li><li>Working Location: City Hall</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days, Monday – Friday (9.00AM – 6:00PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Plan, manage, and oversee audit engagements for a diverse client portfolio, ensuring compliance with standards.</li><li>Review and mentor audit teams, provide training to junior staff.</li><li>Engage with clients to understand business dynamics, identify risks, and offer recommendations.</li><li>Prepare and present high-quality audit reports and financial statements.</li><li>Participate in improving audit quality and processes.</li><li>Contribute to business development, including proposal writing and presentations.</li><li>Other duties assigned by Partner and HODs.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Accountancy/Finance.</li><li>Min 5 years of relevant experience.</li><li>Holds a professional accountancy qualification (CA) or currently studying towards it.</li><li>Proven track record in managing multiple audit engagements.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75376 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
